 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45feac80ccf40f482c6ac7cdeafd9ccb89b98e36","tid":2494934,"uid":4503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"其實納粹 當年都有呢個優生學要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n種族優生（Racial hygiene），是一種由政府挑選出公認最強健、聰明和有道德的人來培育下一代的制度，與公共衛生和優生學有密切關聯。過去為達成目的曾用的手段包括放逐、隔離、強制絕育，或甚至滅絕各種不同的精神障礙、人種、身體殘疾、犯罪記錄和宗教信仰的人或團體。<br />\n<br />\n利用社會措施來嘗試保留或加強某些生物特性的想法，最初是由法蘭西斯&middot;高爾頓在1869年提出，不久後這被稱為優生學。20世紀初，認為人類遺傳因子必須受到管制，或許用強制性的方法，的想法開始盛行，並受到許多主流政治和科學人士的支持，包括溫斯頓&middot;邱吉爾、亞歷山大&middot;格拉漢姆&middot;貝爾和瑪麗&middot;斯托普斯（英語：Marie Stopes）等。[來源請求]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLink<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E5%84%AA%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E5%2584%25AA%25E7%2594%259F&d=ZGEEaRoo4ZESsTiVlrSVptTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=1529cf7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E5%84%AA%E7%94%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26cd8ff92a5b76b42e88ce36e1c30c5c15e955a","tid":2494934,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b367f11352f9c7ace9bacb6995f815b1317a7a9f","tid":2494934,"uid":84791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"139621bc89fedfb75e108490b0a77f40fd8655b8","tid":2494934,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fee339aa3b9efb43a961ced9aa0ba0d59667682","tid":2494934,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T02:38:14.000Z","msg":"鬼叫咁多棄養<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:04:57.000Z","msg":"可能遲啲強制1男娶2女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"已經唔夠分仲要一男娶兩女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donn